- "mañana" → tomorrow; "esta semana" → Mon–Sun of current week
- Named holidays → exact dates above
- Single date → startDate=endDate=that date
- No month specified ("el día 5") → use PREVIOUS CONTEXT month or current month
- Relative refs ("esa semana", "Y empezando el...") → resolve from PREVIOUS CONTEXT
' + prevContext + '
SCHEMA (include ALL keys, null if unused):
{"action":"<action>","payload":{"startDate":"YYYY-MM-DD","endDate":"YYYY-MM-DD","date":"YYYY-MM-DD","roomId":null,"roomName":"","price":null,"bookingId":null,"guests":null,"nombre":null,"email":null,"telefono":null,"hora":null,"name":null,"note":null},"isDestructive":false,"confirmationMessage":"","humanReadableSummary":"<one sentence in Spanish>"}

COMMAND: ' + text;

} else {
  claudePrompt = 'You are an API router. Output ONLY JSON.
